posts.subject: can't archive/download posts on millchan
posts.body:
I keep getting this error when I archive/download posts from millchan. I've already updated and check files in ZeroHello. I've also reinstalled ZeroNet on my computer on a different folder/drive. I was able to replicate the same error on my phone. I'm running ZeroNet 0.7.1

This is the following error:

Internal error: TypeError: actionBigfileUploadInit() takes 4 positional arguments but 5 were given
UiWebsocket.py line 79 > UiWebsocket.py line 232 > MergerSite/MergerSitePlugin.py line 177 > MergerSite/MergerSitePlugin.py line 147
